" <comment>上記のオプションは電源管理機能が有効にする場合だけなく、システムのすべてのCPUを有効にするために必要かもしれません</comment>\n"

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><title>
#: en/kernel-config.xml:478
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "x86 High Memory support"
msgstr "x86のハイメモリサポート"

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/kernel-config.xml:482
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Due to limitations in the 32-bit address space of the x86 architecture, a\n"
"kernel with default configuration can only support up to 896mb RAM. If your\n"
"system has more memory, only the first 896mb will be visible, unless you enable\n"
"high memory support.\n"
